.AVIATION...
(12Z TAFS)
Issued at 321 AM PST Tue Dec 10 2024

Currently VFR at terminals thanks to decent low level mixing
(offshore flow) and clear skies. One potential spoiler this
morning is fog developing at KSTS. When the winds tanked earlier
fog briefly formed and quickly cleared as winds picked up. Still
low chance (10-20%) for fog so kept tempo in.

